Experience with enterprise level monitoring platforms.
 
Knowledge of DHCP and DNS (bind) services, SMTP, NTP.
 
Experience in security policy and access controls for networks, systems, and users, LDAP.
 
High Availability design, performance analysis and deployment experience.
 
Knowledgeable about SAN performance and layout.
 
Deep knowledge of Centos/Redhat administration.
 
Familiarity with VMware Virtualization
 
Experience with problem identification, isolation, and resolution.
 
